## <a id='other'></a> Using <%= vars.product_short %> Components

In addition to apps, <%= vars.product_short %> supports single sign-on for components of <%= vars.app_runtime_full %>,
including <%= vars.ops_manager %> and Apps Manager.
This enables users already managed in an external IdP to sign into
VMware Tanzu services.


Refer to the following pages for instructions on configuring <%= vars.product_short %> to enable users
in an external identity store to access <%= vars.app_runtime_full %> components:

* <%= vars.ops_manager %>, on [Amazon Web Services](http://docs.pivotal.io/pivotalcf/customizing/cloudform-om-config.html#idp),
[vSphere](http://docs.pivotal.io/pivotalcf/customizing/vsphere-config.html#idp),
or [OpenStack](http://docs.pivotal.io/pivotalcf/customizing/openstack-om-config.html#idp)

* [Apps Manager](http://docs.pivotal.io/pivotalcf/opsguide/auth-sso.html)
